text: Xiangyang Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Xunyang District, Jiujiang, Jiangxi, China, located in Jiujiang Economic and Technological Development Zone. , it has 8 residential communities and 7 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Jiangxi == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Jiangxi Category:Jiujiang
title: Xiangyang Subdistrict, Jiujiang
